# 16. Find the service which makes it possible to run specific tasks following a regular
# schedule

cron

# example:

# typing in terminal: $ crontab -e
# next -> insert via selected editor in the end of document:
# */2 * * * * date >> $HOME/example_cron.txt

# after every 2 minutes if file '$HOME/example_cron.txt'
# will be added current data at moment of adding
